<br>
Rapid Feign - Agree. <br>
<br>
Ambi Dex - Think it would be about 2-3% total damage increase.<br>
<br>
Critical Mend - 1 in 4 mends to heal for 50%. Heh this I would get before RF3.<br>
<br>
Dragon Punch - Again nice to have to interrupt casters while xp'ing.<br>
<br>
My current needs dictate being a better xp'er, to this end Durability, Stability, and Agility are better practical choices. While some class skills are nice, they do not benefit me as a group or solo xp gainer.<br>
<br>
